🔥 Root Cause
Your agent calls tool_router with arguments, but your function expects a single JSON string param named input_data.
From logs:
additional_kwargs={'tool_calls': [{
  'function': {
    'arguments': '{"service":"communication","task_type":"search_contacts","data":"{\\"name\\":\\"Tushar\\"}","scheduled":false,"scheduled_at":"","query":"try again now for 1:23am"}',
    'name': 'tool_router'
  }
}]}
So the model is calling:
tool_router({
  "service": "communication",
  "task_type": "search_contacts",
  "data": "{\"name\":\"Tushar\"}",
  "scheduled": false,
  "scheduled_at": "",
  "query": "try again now for 1:23am"
})
But your function signature is:
@tool
def tool_router(input_data: str) -> Dict[str, Any]:



You are making this mistake
don't make this mistake

